{"tid":2197959,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"水炮車指揮官改認現場有市民","createTime":"2020-09-11T04:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T04:34:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c276f9a97efddd09e04490f28f72310eec87a557","tid":2197959,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/EUBYX7VJPZD5VJLRDGTOWY6PEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FEUBYX7VJPZD5VJLRDGTOWY6PEM%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FMZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=72b4fc49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FEUBYX7VJPZD5VJLRDGTOWY6PEM%2F&h=1b91769a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/EUBYX7VJPZD5VJLRDGTOWY6PEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n水炮車指揮官改認現場有市民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9J-gYRjVsdIhZo0H9itLA0ihqX8=/1028x685/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VW6YGEEUINEKVH2CUXRRYN26FY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9J-gYRjVsdIhZo0H9itLA0ihqX8%3D%2F1028x685%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVW6YGEEUINEKVH2CUXRRYN26FY.jpg&h=9121c701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n灣仔區域法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8.31港島嚴重警民衝突中，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警指記者「冇證」<br />\n<br />\n水炮車指揮官伍國雄供稱，當晚他沿軒尼詩道掃蕩，利用水炮車的擴音裝置警告示威者散開及錄影。資深大律師潘熙盤問時指，當日是警方首次在港島使用水炮車，市民或感新鮮及好奇。伍同意當日有不少記者拍攝水炮車，但不同意有市民追着水炮車拍攝，「暴動現場點會有市民啫？」<br />\n<br />\n辯方播片，顯示有西裝打呔男士旁觀，另有女士「拎住手機追水炮車影相」，街邊亦有尋常衣着的人。辯方問伍：「你唔會覺得佢哋係示威者啦，啱唔啱？」伍同意。<br />\n<br />\n另外，拘捕首被告。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n余德穎等八名被告被控於在灣仔軒尼詩道及盧押道一帶參與暴動。案件下周一續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC12/20"},{"pid":"a0375b6a1f3d12b02bd576f0dfeccec43d130b91","tid":2197959,"uid":269202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"照警察所講, 所有清真寺南亞都係暴徒"},{"pid":"b2dda7747d69fc7e0e11904f3b62fde7c3e0859e","tid":2197959,"uid":249979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:27:47.000Z","msg":"全世界所有人都係暴徒<br />\n除非你係黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddad3dfbc2e653e3878176f365f50d742b9928e9","tid":2197959,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"現場狗隻甚多"}]}